# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Platform frontend environment (Next.js)
#
# Copy to `.env.local` for local dev, or set in your host (Cloudflare Pages)
# build settings. Only NEXT_PUBLIC_* vars are exposed to the browser bundle.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Sepolia JSON-RPC endpoint used for read calls and as the default transport.
# Get a free one from Alchemy / Infura. If omitted, a public endpoint is used
# (works but may rate-limit). Wallet writes always go through the user's wallet.
NEXT_PUBLIC_SEPOLIA_RPC_URL=""
